text: Carl Maria Peter Ferdinand Philipp Albrecht Joseph Michael Pius Konrad Robert Ulrich Herzog von Württemberg (1 August 1936 – 7 June 2022) was head of the House of Württemberg from 1975 until his death in 2022. Carl died in a hospital in Ravensburg, Germany on 7 June 2022 at the age of 85.Décès de Carl de Wurtemberg : le prétendant au trône et époux de Diane d’Orléans avait 85 ans ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2022 deaths Category:German dukes and duchesses
